description:
code based on the IEC 60191 code to identify the die.
The code has the form A-XBCC-Dnn/mmm, where |A is a shape class code |X is a code for the encapsulation material |B is a terminal position code |CC is the body style code|D is the terminal shape code |nn is the number of terminals |mmm is a sequence number to distiguish uniquely dies whose codes would otherwise be identical.
